{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- we had an-- we called it-- how we called it again?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a funny word for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wouldn't come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, that was a package where all secret papers were in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For instance, passports of Jewish people and the names where they were hidden, et cetera-- so that was deadly dangerous, that package.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for that reason, we moved it very often, from one house to the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day, my husband came to-- a friend of ours from our organization, Jan Bartelsman, was caught.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the last thing we knew that he had the package.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But his wife told us that he had brought it the night before-- he was-- he happened to bring it to his mother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we knew the package, as we called it-- which was red hot dangerous-- that it was with his mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when he was caught, there was always a chance that they would go to all his family members.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband raced to, on the bicycle, to his mother, who lived in the same village, and said, I know you have the package.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Give it to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll hide it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's too dangerous to be with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he brought that back and, with a Jewish man who was hidden with us, they dug a hole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when-- they didn't tell me anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was in-- they had wrapped it in tar paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I saw them digging there in the garden and I thought, well, what are they doing there?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were always stressed with fear and all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I thought, what are they doing there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Something I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said what are you doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
